<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTM1.2.17">
<l>paruva nirampāmē pārellā muyya</l>
<l>tiruviṉ vaṭivokkun tēvaki peṟṟa</l>
<l>vuruvu kariya voḷimaṇi vaṇṇaṉ</l>
<l>puruva miruntavā kāṇīrē pūṇmulai yīrvantu kāṇīrē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>You with jewelled breasts, see the quality of the eyebrows of him,</l>
<l>who is the colour of a beautiful, bright, dark sapphire,</l>
<l>who was begotten by Devakī, who is equal in beauty to Tiru,</l>
<l>in order to save the whole world just when [he] reached the fullness of youth.  Come and see!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
